# ESP32 Motor Controller PCB

## Overview

This project showcases a custom **2-layer PCB** designed in **KiCad 9** for an ESP32-based embedded control system intended for robotics and motor control applications.

The board integrates power regulation, motor driver circuitry, communication interfaces, and expansion headers into a compact PCB layout suitable for embedded development and rapid prototyping.

---

## Features

- 2-Layer PCB Design
- ESP32 DevKit Integration
- Motor Driver Interface
- On-board Power Regulation
- JST Battery Connector
- Programming Header
- Expansion Headers
- Power Switch
- Reverse Polarity Protection
- Decoupling Capacitors
- Compact Component Placement
- 3D Mechanical Model (STEP)

